                        <additions>
                            <p>A few marginalia occur; among the younger ones one written by <name
                                    type="person" key="ThoTor001">Torfæus</name> on fol. 217r can be
                                noted. It reads: <q xml:lang="da">Da er hun Nu denn afften som jeg
                                    Thormod Torfuesson leser hende 132 Aar thoe Maaned och sexs dage
                                    gammel, efftersom vi nu skriffuer 1675 den 30 November som er
                                    Sancti Andrea dag.</q>
                            </p>
                        </additions>
